    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It has been incredibly well-loved and pampered\u2014not a single speck of dust or a scratch to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone to take it on a new adventure. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you've found it. Drop me a message, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
