    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3, meticulously maintained and free of the common S65 V8 weak points. This unit features a 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a factory-spec variable M differential. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement with VAC coated units and ARP hardware, alongside new throttle actuators. The chassis exhibits zero subframe fatigue, retaining its original torsional rigidity and sharp handling characteristics thanks to a pristine EDC-equipped suspension. The paint finish shows exceptional depth, and the interior demonstrates minimal wear on the bolsters, reflecting a strictly garaged life. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
